headline: Assessing Ingersoll Rand (IR) Valuation After Q4 Beat And 2026 Growth Outlook
summary: Ingersoll Rand (IR) stock moved after the company reported fourth quarter 2025 results that topped Wall Street forecasts on revenue and adjusted earnings, alongside full year 2026 guidance and fresh capital return updates. See our latest analysis for Ingersoll Rand. The latest move takes Ingersoll Rand’s share price to $98.52, with a 30 day share price return of 11.75% and a 90 day share price return of 33.73%. The 5 year total shareholder return of 125.62% points to strong longer term...
